&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
醍醐寺の弁天堂と橋。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">The Bentendo Temple and bridge at Daigo-ji Temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R04211.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Spring on the River・大堰川の春</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210327/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Spring on the River・大堰川の春" /><published>2021-03-27T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-27T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/oigawa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210327/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
