&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Boats" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html">Beautiful day for taking a ride on the Katsura (Oi) River to watch the cherry blossoms.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R04109.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Cherry Blossom Season・桜の季節</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210326/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Cherry Blossom Season・桜の季節 " /><published>2021-03-26T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-26T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210326/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
